{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_13_01",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『地下闘技場最強アイドルトーナメント』後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……。……うん、いい感じだ\n後もう少し、ターンを速くすれば……もっと……",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}君、どうしたの？　さっきから\n隅っこで突っ立ってるけど、じっと見てるだけ？",
      "startTime": 16.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕としては、新しいステップの感想を\n聞かせてほしいんだけど",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵の練習する姿が、あまりに熱心だったから\n邪魔をしたくなかったんだ。お疲れ様、葵",
      "startTime": 28.2602171246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、新しいステップの感想だけど……\n俺の目には完璧に見えたよ。百点だと思う",
      "startTime": 36.1015867551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。僕としてはまだ八十点くらいかな\nターンに入るタイミングがまだ甘いよ",
      "startTime": 45.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今の時点で八十点なら十分じゃないか\n相変わらず自分に厳しいな、葵は",
      "startTime": 52.6538086255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう少し軽めの練習でもいいと思うけどな\n追い込み方が、まるで本番直前みたいなハードさだぞ",
      "startTime": 60.1204752922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n本番直前だよ。明日が本番なんだから",
      "startTime": 65.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7996.666666700008,
          "startTime": 73.23
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？　嘘だろ、まさか俺が予定を勘違い……\nしてないな。次のLizNoirのライブは来月だぞ",
      "startTime": 73.9563258807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。リズノワは来月だけど、僕の方は明日なんだ\n僕、また例の地下闘技場のライブに招待されたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 84.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "また招待されたでしょ？　……って、俺は初耳だよ\n細かいことはともかく、またアレに出るつもりなのか？",
      "startTime": 93.1874142011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど。あれ？　僕、まきびし丸君……\nじゃなくて、君に伝えてなかったっけ？",
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと待ってくれ、今なんて言った？\n俺がまきびし丸？　どうしてそのことを知ってるんだ？",
      "startTime": 108.1640859396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣から聞いたんだ\n君もアイドルになりたかったなんて、知らなかったよ",
      "startTime": 114.2625600498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、あの日、地下闘技場最強アイドルトーナメントで）\n（俺は一度だけ、覆面アイドル『まきびし丸』になった）",
      "startTime": 123.1328552565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（出来ることなら知られたくない、俺の秘密だ）\n（……もう秘密じゃなくなってるけど）",
      "startTime": 131.5328608514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳で、明日は地下闘技場に行くって今伝えたよ\nいいよね？　まきびし丸君",
      "startTime": 138.6371966259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "その名前で呼ぶのは止めてほしいんだけど……\nとにかく、これだけは確認させてくれ",
      "startTime": 144.5392780623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "地下闘技場には、もちろん観客として行くんだよな？\nまさかとは思うけど、出演はしない……よな？",
      "startTime": 151.8234985671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そんなの聞くまでもないだろう？",
      "startTime": 156.0059446018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……そうだよな、事務所に内緒で\nBIG4のアイドルが二度もそんなこと――",
      "startTime": 162.7307445781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "今度は僕一人で出場するんだ\nソロのバトルなんてめったにないからね。楽しみだよ",
      "startTime": 168.3333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがだよ、葵\nいつだって葵は俺の予想を、軽々と飛び越えていくな",
      "startTime": 174.6706828291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。君に褒められるとやる気が出るよ\n地下闘技場でのバトル、絶対に勝つから",
      "startTime": 182.6333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "褒めてないんだけど……はぁ、仕方ない。でも今後は\n一人で勝手に決めないで、俺に相談すること。いいか？",
      "startTime": 191.5430630686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった。ところで、続きを話してもいい？\n僕がまた地下闘技場でバトルをする理由なんだけど",
      "startTime": 201.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "本当に分かってるのか怪しいけど……\nまぁいい、続けてくれ。理由は俺も気になる",
      "startTime": 208.2014981908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "前回のライブで仲良くなったアイドルがいてね\nその子に挑戦されたんだ",
      "startTime": 215.6333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "次は一対一で、ライブバトルをしようって\nバトルを挑まれたら、逃げる訳にはいかないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 222.7132594809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "葵がそこまで言うからには\n何を言っても止められないだろうな……",
      "startTime": 228.8438790324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。でも俺もついて行く\n葵がステージに上がって騒ぎになったら、大事だからな",
      "startTime": 235.2105456991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいよ。でも僕一人交じったくらいで\n騒ぎになんてならないよ。心配性だね、君は",
      "startTime": 243.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "葵はもっと心配した方がいいと思うけどな……\nBIG4なんだぞ？　……はぁ",
      "startTime": 252.0050314128,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5579.432628799964,
          "startTime": 257.5844640416
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 256.2511347773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.4511308355
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.4511308355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちが上がるよね、地下闘技場のこの雰囲気\nやっぱり来て良かったよ",
      "startTime": 263.033333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
